	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I use a 200mhz dev pc for most things, small form factor with parallel and serial ports moved to the front for ease of access. A copynes works great for things, although I still need to build a devcart for it. I may just get bunnyboy's cart when it becomes available.
<br />As for the programming itself, I just use a text-editor. Haven't done too much NES programming due to a lack of free time though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
