		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I use a simple text editor (vi), fce ultra, and wine (to emulate nintendulator and yy-chr) on my Dell box running Linux.  This has worked well for me.  I have an eprom burner but am waiting until I write something worth burning before I give that a spin.  Like everyone else here .... time is an issue.

		

